{"tid":2247913,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"「點新聞」分析南區樓盤 卻屈黃之鋒住貝沙灣","createTime":"2020-10-18T08:30:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-18T12:31:57.000Z","uid":240362,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"66b95ccd0ba716b7fc07cbf3663869cefbdb17b9","tid":2247913,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T08:30:38.000Z","msg":"由中聯辦控制嘅《大公報》、大公文匯集團高層持股的網媒「點新聞」，近日喺一個網上節目請嚟風水師周璞初，分析南區樓盤，最終卻變成講吓黃之鋒喺南區嘅住所啱唔啱佢命格。片中一名自稱Sophia嘅女主持話，黃之鋒原本住喺海怡半島，但最近就「好似忽然富貴，搬去貝沙灣喎」，再由風水師以風水命理，解釋一番，話點解貝沙灣適合黃之鋒居住。<br />\n<br />\n黃之鋒今日睇咗呢段由朋友傳畀佢嘅片後，忍唔住要喺Facebook寫返句：「到底我睇咗啲乜.jpg」，並hashtag「人一藍腦變殘」，強調自己經唔知講咗幾多千百萬次，根本從來冇住貝沙灣，亦都冇任何貝沙灣物業，似乎對於藍絲呢類屈得就屈嘅節目，深表無奈。<br />\n<br />\n有網友洞悉藍絲夾硬老屈嘅陰謀，「一個大話講100次，啲人就以為係真㗎嘛」、「可能是洗腦效應，不過都要D（啲）人無腦先洗到」；另亦有人好阿Q，「睇完笑咗，（黃）問佢哋收返廣告費」、「好好笑，水洗都唔清，但個fact對佢哋（藍媒）嚟講真係唔重要」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201018/LFHS5FIF6ZCPVN4C7LCUII65XM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201018%2FLFHS5FIF6ZCPVN4C7LCUII65XM%2F&d=lXXpVpUBFe4etFVyslLGPRZ9qy%2BOiqBAJcOKDokr%2FlY%3D&h=4b0aaaa4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201018%2FLFHS5FIF6ZCPVN4C7LCUII65XM%2F&h=82fa7c31\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201018/LFHS5FIF6ZCPVN4C7LCUII65XM/</a>"},{"pid":"67d8f16e2ff24cd1ae18e02a56a5a9fb187252a1","tid":2247913,"uid":264245,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T08:32:05.000Z","msg":"藍絲買返座落佢名咪得囉<br />\n肯買未<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9873cf66e6c30cbf124f2429f1bef336b2aa27ab","tid":2247913,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T08:41:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afcd7e56ea7bac21ba3ee962ab91e6da